<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 12:29:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于中美国内旅游需求下降，万豪下调2024年盈利预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/marriott-lowers-2024-profit-forecast-us-china-domestic-tourism-drags-2024-11-04/</link><description>由于美国和中国的国内旅游需求依然疲弱，万豪国际集团周一下调了年度盈利预期，导致其股价在盘前交易中下跌 4.1%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 12:12:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/marriott-lowers-2024-profit-forecast-us-china-domestic-tourism-drags-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：爱荷华州和就业数据的异常值造成混乱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-04/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 11:15:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的关税将重新调整贸易流动、提高成本并招致报复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/trumps-tariffs-would-reorder-trade-flows-raise-costs-draw-retaliation-2024-11-04/</link><description>农业团体担心巴西和阿根廷的出口市场遭受损失。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 11:11:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/trumps-tariffs-would-reorder-trade-flows-raise-costs-draw-retaliation-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>以色列对伊朗的袭击引发了人们对空射弹道导弹的兴趣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israels-strikes-iran-spark-interest-air-launched-ballistic-missiles-2024-11-04/</link><description>以色列在对伊朗的空袭中有效地使用空射弹道导弹，预计将激起其他国家购买这些武器的兴趣，而大多数大国都避免购买这些武器，转而使用巡航导弹和滑翔炸弹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 11:02:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israels-strikes-iran-spark-interest-air-launched-ballistic-missiles-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国石化与TotalEnergies签署为期15年的液化天然气交易协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-sinopec-signs-agreement-15-yr-lng-deal-with-totalenergies-2024-11-04/</link><description>中国国有石油天然气巨头中石化周一表示，已签署协议，从 2028 年开始，为期 15 年，每年从 TotalEnergies 购买 200 万吨液化天然气。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 10:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-sinopec-signs-agreement-15-yr-lng-deal-with-totalenergies-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>商务部表示，中国将就欧盟电动汽车最终裁决向世贸组织提起诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-file-lawsuit-with-wto-against-eus-final-ev-ruling-commerce-ministry-says-2024-11-04/</link><description>中国商务部周一表示，决定就欧盟对中国产电动汽车的最终反补贴措施向世贸组织提起诉讼。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 10:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-file-lawsuit-with-wto-against-eus-final-ev-ruling-commerce-ministry-says-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>英国石油公司首席执行官表示，中东紧张局势是能源市场面临的首要风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/mideast-tensions-top-risk-facing-energy-markets-says-bp-ceo-2024-11-04/</link><description>英国石油公司首席执行官默里·奥金克洛斯在阿布扎比举行的一次行业活动中表示，中东紧张局势是能源市场面临的最大风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 10:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/mideast-tensions-top-risk-facing-energy-markets-says-bp-ceo-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉 10 月份中国制造电动汽车销量同比下降 5.3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-oct-china-made-ev-sales-fall-53-yy-2024-11-04/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周一的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉10月份销售了68,280辆中国制造的电动汽车，同比下降5.3%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 09:36:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-oct-china-made-ev-sales-fall-53-yy-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，马来西亚向越南抱怨南海珊瑚礁扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-complains-vietnam-over-south-china-sea-reef-expansion-sources-say-2024-11-04/</link><description>两名官员告诉路透社，马来西亚已就越南涉嫌扩张南海珊瑚礁向越南发出投诉信，两国均声称拥有该珊瑚礁，这是罕见的不涉及中国的双边升级。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 08:53:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-complains-vietnam-over-south-china-sea-reef-expansion-sources-say-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车10月销量同比增长3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-october-sales-rise-3-year-on-year-2024-11-04/</link><description>总部位于瑞典的汽车制造商沃尔沃汽车周一表示，10 月份沃尔沃汽车销量同比增长 3%，达到 61,686 辆，主要得益于全电动和插电式混合动力车型在欧洲销量的增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 08:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-october-sales-rise-3-year-on-year-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>法国家庭因涉嫌未能删除有害内容而起诉 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/french-families-sue-tiktok-over-alleged-failure-remove-harmful-content-2024-11-04/</link><description>七个法国家庭的律师周一表示，他们对社交媒体巨头 TikTok 提起诉讼，指控该平台让他们的青春期孩子接触有害内容，导致其中两人在 15 岁时自杀。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 07:41:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/french-families-sue-tiktok-over-alleged-failure-remove-harmful-content-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>缅甸军政府主席将自夺权以来首次访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-junta-chief-make-first-china-visit-since-seizing-power-2024-11-04/</link><description>官方媒体周一称，缅甸军政府领导人敏昂莱将于本周前往中国参加地区峰会，这是这位四面楚歌的高级将领自 2021 年政变中夺取政权以来首次访问这个有影响力的邻国。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 04:54:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-junta-chief-make-first-china-visit-since-seizing-power-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国蔚来汽车计划仅在海外销售其首款混合动力汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-plans-sell-its-first-hybrid-car-overseas-only-sources-say-2024-11-04/</link><description>据两位知情人士透露，中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车计划于 2026 年推出首款混合动力车型，并且仅在中东、北非和欧洲等海外市场销售。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 04:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-plans-sell-its-first-hybrid-car-overseas-only-sources-say-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>法国捍卫欧盟，中国敦促欧盟提出令人满意的电动汽车贸易解决方案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-france-get-eu-arrive-palatable-ev-solution-2024-11-03/</link><description>中国敦促法国推动欧盟委员会达成欧洲和中国电动汽车行业都能接受的解决方案，而法国则表示，在推动推翻白兰地关税的过程中，欧盟不会在关键问题上让步。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 23:34:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-france-get-eu-arrive-palatable-ev-solution-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国太阳能企业进入美国关税未触及的领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-solar-firms-ever-nimble-go-further-afield-where-us-tariffs-dont-reach-2024-11-03/</link><description>越南的一些中资太阳能工厂正在减产并解雇工人，而老挝和印度尼西亚的新工厂也如雨后春笋般涌现。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-solar-firms-ever-nimble-go-further-afield-where-us-tariffs-dont-reach-2024-11-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>